name: It's An Older Code
Lore: 'Even though Vader allowed the stolen shuttle Tydirium to land on Endor, he had a plan to deal with the Rebels.',
Text: 'USED: If opponent just landed a starship at an exterior site, you may deploy up to three related sites from your Reserve Deck; reshuffle.LOST: Use 2 Force to ''scan'' (reveal) opponent''s hand. You may place one starship you find there in opponent''s Used Pile.',
